8. Design Decisions & Rationale
1.	Chose Tkinter because it is built into Python and lightweight.
2.	Used random and string modules to generate secure passwords.
3.	Did not use database/storage to protect user privacy.
4.	Chose a dark UI theme to reduce eye strain and look modern.
________________________________________
9. Implementation Details
Programming Language: Python
Library Used: Tkinter (GUI)
Supporting Libraries:
•	random
•	string
The password is generated using:
string.ascii_letters + string.digits + "!@#$%^&*"
Each button in the GUI is connected to a function such as:
•	generate_password()
•	generate_multiple()
•	copy_password()
